:13,"body":16,"filePath":17,"digest":18,"deferredRender":19},{"title":14,"excerpt":15},"Public Speaker Profile","My public speaker profile.","## Profile Picture(s)\n\n\u003Cimg src=\"/static/notes/speaker_profile_square.jpeg\" alt=\"Profile Picture\" width=\"512\" height=\"512\" />\n\n[Full size (Square)](/static/notes/speaker_profile_square.jpeg) · [Full size (not cropped)](/static/notes/speaker_profile_full.jpeg)\n\n## Social Links\n\n| Platform | URL |\n|---|---|\n| Twitter | https://twitter.com/calganaygun |\n| GitHub | https://github.com/calganaygun |\n| Developer Profile | https://g.dev/calgan |\n| LinkedIn | https://linkedin.com/in/calganaygun |\n\n## Titles\n\n- DevOps Lead at FinalCheck\n- Google Developer Expert on Google Cloud\n\n## Biography\n\nÇalgan Aygün is a Warsaw-based DevOps Lead at FinalCheck. As a Google Developer Expert (GDE) on Google Cloud, he focuses on building scalable, robust infrastructure. His professional background spans fintech, data analytics, OSINT and cyber security.\n\nAn active public speaker and former community organizer, he remains deeply involved in the tech ecosystem.\n\nHe also provides independent consultancy services for AI and DevSecOps. Outside of his professional focus, he is a dedicated ham radio enthusiast and amateur photographer.","src/content/notes/speaker-profile.mdx","9ebc60393fa480e6",true]